          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  The SPIRAL facility."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "PRJFS"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The radioactive beam of Ar-44 has been",
                " produced through the projectile fragmentation of a",
                " 66 A*MeV Ca-48 primary beam of about 200 pnA intensity",
                " in a thick carbon target located at the underground",
                " production cave of SPIRAL."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "SILI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Protons were detected at forward",
                "angles(between 110- and 170-degree) using the eight",
                "highly segmented MUST telescopes.The first stage of a",
                "MUST module consists in a 300-mum thick, 60*60 mm**2",
                "double sided Si-strip detector, each strip was backed",
                "by a lithium drifted silicon diode-SiLi of",
                "approximately 3 mm thickness."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The beam-like transfer products were selected",
                "by the SPEG spectrometer."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The tracking of the secondary beams was achieved",
                "by a position sensitive gas filled detector CATS."
              ]
            }
          ],
